RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 5 1/2F All Weather Track CR: 67. Maiden Claiming Purse 21000. FOR MAIDENS, FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Weight, 122 lbs. Claiming Price $12,500.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: FROSTED FAITH dueled inside GRANDE SOIREE while racing in the two path then drew off under left-handed urging in the lane. WHEATSHEAF raced in the clear off the duel in the two path, angled four wide near the quarter pole, could not keep pace with the winner in upper stretch and churned on to gain the place. GRANDE SOIREE dueled outside of the winner to upper stretch, could not keep pace from there, continued on the left lead in the lane, lugged in leaving the eighth pole and lost the show late. ROCK SOLID WORDS failed to menace while racing three wide. MUD BUG steadied at the start, dropped far back in the two path and was never involved. WILLWORKFORFOOD played no factor while racing four wide. QUEEN DE LA CREME was through early and was eased in the lane.
